<td class="mbox-text" style="">Look up <i><b><a href="http://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/debit_card" class="extiw" title="wiktionary:debit card">debit card</a></b></i> in<br />
<a href="/wiki/Wiktionary" title="Wiktionary">Wiktionary</a>, the free dictionary.</td>
</tr>
